SELECT [b].[Id], [b].[Author], [b].[Category], [b].[CreationTime], [b].[CreatorUserId], [b].[DeleterUserId], [b].[DeletionTime], [b].[Description], [b].[Frequency], [b].[ImageId], [b].[ImageUrl], [b].[IsDeleted], [b].[Isbn10], [b].[Isbn13], [b].[LastModificationTime], [b].[LastModifierUserId], [b].[Number_Avaliable], [b].[PublishedDate], [b].[Title], [b].[uniqueId], [f].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[BookId], [t].[CreationTime], [t].[CreatorUserId], [t].[DeleterUserId], [t].[DeletionTime], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[LastModificationTime], [t].[LastModifierUserId], [t].[Message], [t].[rating], [f].[FileExtention], [f].[FileLength], [f].[FilePath], [f].[Filename]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
LEFT JOIN [Files] AS [f] ON [b].[ImageId] = [f].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[BookId], [c].[CreationTime], [c].[CreatorUserId], [c].[DeleterUserId], [c].[DeletionTime], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[LastModificationTime], [c].[LastModifierUserId], [c].[Message], [c].[rating]
    FROM [Comment] AS [c]
    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [c].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t] ON [b].[Id] = [t].[BookId]
WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [b].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND ([b].[Title] LIKE @__searchTerm_0_contains ESCAPE N'\' OR [b].[Isbn10] LIKE @__searchTerm_0_contains ESCAPE N'\' OR [b].[Isbn13] LIKE @__searchTerm_0_contains ESCAPE N'\' OR [b].[Category] LIKE @__searchTerm_0_contains ESCAPE N'\' OR [b].[Author] LIKE @__searchTerm_0_contains ESCAPE N'\')

INFO  2024-04-12 13:39:35,859 [orker] oft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command - Executed DbCommand (33ms) [Parameters=[@__ef_filter__p_0='?' (DbType = Boolean), @__searchTerm_0_contains='?' (Size = 4000)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [b].[Id], [b].[Author], [b].[Category], [b].[CreationTime], [b].[CreatorUserId], [b].[DeleterUserId], [b].[DeletionTime], [b].[Description], [b].[Frequency], [b].[ImageId], [b].[ImageUrl], [b].[IsDeleted], [b].[Isbn10], [b].[Isbn13], [b].[LastModificationTime], [b].[LastModifierUserId], [b].[Number_Avaliable], [b].[PublishedDate], [b].[Title], [b].[uniqueId], [f].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[BookId], [t].[CreationTime], [t].[CreatorUserId], [t].[DeleterUserId], [t].[DeletionTime], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[LastModificationTime], [t].[LastModifierUserId], [t].[Message], [t].[rating], [f].[FileExtention], [f].[FileLength], [f].[FilePath], [f].[Filename]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
LEFT JOIN [Files] AS [f] ON [b].[ImageId] = [f].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[BookId], [c].[CreationTime], [c].[CreatorUserId], [c].[DeleterUserId], [c].[DeletionTime], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[LastModificationTime], [c].[LastModifierUserId], [c].[Message], [c].[rating]
    FROM [Comment] AS [c]

SELECT [b].[Id], [b].[Author], [b].[Category], [b].[CreationTime], [b].[CreatorUserId], [b].[DeleterUserId], [b].[DeletionTime], [b].[Description], [b].[Frequency], [b].[ImageId], [b].[ImageUrl], [b].[IsDeleted], [b].[Isbn10], [b].[Isbn13], [b].[LastModificationTime], [b].[LastModifierUserId], [b].[Number_Avaliable], [b].[PublishedDate], [b].[Title], [b].[uniqueId], [f].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[BookId], [t].[CreationTime], [t].[CreatorUserId], [t].[DeleterUserId], [t].[DeletionTime], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[LastModificationTime], [t].[LastModifierUserId], [t].[Message], [t].[rating], [f].[FileExtention], [f].[FileLength], [f].[FilePath], [f].[Filename]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
LEFT JOIN [Files] AS [f] ON [b].[ImageId] = [f].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[BookId], [c].[CreationTime], [c].[CreatorUserId], [c].[DeleterUserId], [c].[DeletionTime], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[LastModificationTime], [c].[LastModifierUserId], [c].[Message], [c].[rating]

    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [c].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t] ON [b].[Id] = [t].[BookId]

ORDER BY [a].[Priority] DESC, [a].[TryCount], [a].[NextTryTime]
